🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

items.text:
Projekt: Kurzfilm „Zwischen Schatten und Licht“

Drehzeit: Januar 2026

Ort: Umkreis von 200 km von Nordhorn 

Format: Kurzfilm

Gesuchte Rollen:

1️⃣ Lucy

 • Spielalter: 26

 • Charakter: Nett, liebevoll, beste Freundin von Stella, loyal und immer unterstützend

 • Schauspielerfahrung von Vorteil aber kein Muss . Newcomer sind ebenso herzlich willkommen 

2️⃣ Nick

 • Spielalter: 25

 • Charakter: Gut aussehend, charismatisch, charmant, Sunnyboy

 • Natürliches, sympathisches Spiel erforderlich

⸻

3️⃣ Felix 

• Spielalter :20

Charakter: ehemaliger Drogemjunkie,Stellas jüngerer Bruder, Geldprobleme 

• Schauspielerfahrungen von Vorteil ,gefragtes Spiel erforderlich 

Story / Kurzbeschreibung:

„Zwischen Schatten und Licht“ erzählt die Geschichte von Stella, die unvermittelt in Gefahr gerät: Victor, dem ihr Bruder Geld aus einem Drogendeal schuldet, lauert ihr auf. Als Stella Nick, einen charismatischen jungen Mann, kennenlernt, funkt es zwischen den beiden — nach einem fast stattgefundenen Kuss stürmt Stella jedoch weg und gerät direkt in die Arme des Bösewichts Victor. Nick beobachtet die Situation und kommt gerade rechtzeitig, als ein heftiger Konflikt zwischen ihm und Victor eskaliert, der in einer Messerstecherei gipfelt. Eine spannende Geschichte über Gefahr, Anziehung und Vertrauen.

⸻

Bewerbung gerne per PN

 • Foto / Porträt

 • Alter / Spielalter

 • Kurzer Lebenslauf / Schauspielerfahrung

 • Showreel

items.text:
Hey guys! We are now enrolling for November classes! There is still some availability in each class, though they're filling quickly. We'd love to have you with us! To register or ask any questions: Please email me at SarahDowlingCasting@gmail.com and put November Classes in the subject line! 

**

We are now registering for our November Zoom workshops and would love for you to join us! Classes are kept intentionally small to maximize the workshop time and provide feedback to each person throughout the class! We look at the back-end of casting software - what a casting director sees when you send your tapes and materials via email or through services like Actors Access, and what the client sees when your material is sent to them! We also cover Scene Study and Improv, and all things business related - auditions, materials, self-tapes etc.  

 I am a 20-year veteran casting director.  My classes are very much tailored to the students who are in them each month. We delve into commercial casting: how to figure out the storyboards and scripts you're sent to audition, how to figure out the tone they're looking for and how to make sure your tapes look like they should for submission. We also do a deep dive into film casting: how to discern the tone and pacing of the script, how to fully inhabit the character and how to make sure your tape captures all of it. 

**This is a business class (taught by a casting director with 20+ yeas experience) offering practical real-life to help actors get representation, widen their representation into other markets, and get more auditions, call backs and bookings.

Please let me know if you have any questions or would like to join us! You can email me at SarahDowlingCasting@gmail.com with any questions or to register! Let me know which day or days are best for you when you email!  Looking forward to working with you! 

Thanks so much,

Sarah

**CASTING CALL – BOULDER, CO**
**Shoot Date:** Saturday, October 26 (6 days away)
**Project:** *Under My Eyelids* – a heartfelt short film about an ex professional skateboarder reflecting on his memories of skateboarding after a severe TBI.

**ROLE:** Kid Cody (Boy, 9–11)
– Curious, brave, and a little shy.
– Comfortable standing or riding on a skateboard (no tricks required).
– Appears in an emotional flashback scene with his mom at a skatepark.

**LOCATION:** Boulder / Louisville area skatepark
**TIME:** Half-day shoot (3–5 hours)
**COMPENSATION:** Non-paid. Food, credit, and footage for reel will be provided.

**TO APPLY:**
Email **baxterdylan7@gmail.com** or call/text **(**970)406-2336 with:
– Child’s name and age
– Recent photo
– Parent/guardian contact information
– Any skateboard experience

This is a warm, character-driven scene about facing fear and finding courage.
— Dylan Lee Baxter
Writer / Director, *Under My Eyelids*

🎤✨ AUDITIONS NOW OPEN! ✨🎭

We’re on the lookout for performers to take part in our Holiday Variety Showcase on Friday 5th December! 🌟

Got a talent or act you’d love to share? Whether you sing, dance, act, juggle, or something completely unique - we want to see it!

🎥 Send us a self-tape of up to 3 minutes of your act to info@paintingelephants.co.uk (this can be a link to Dropbox/YouTube/Google Drive, or just send us a quick WeTransfer!)

📅 Auditions are open 13.10 – 26.10

Don’t miss your chance to be part of a fun, festive night of entertainment with Painting Elephants! 💜

#manchestertheatre #theatre #localtheatre #manchestertheatrecompany #salfordtheatre #paintingelephants #cic #paintingelephantscic #manchesterarts

CASTING CALL for student project shooting in Leeds as part of the Northern Film School

Get in touch to star in our new film. Send us a headshot/showreel and we'll get back to you ASAP 🎬💍

Donttellthegroomfilm@gmail.com ✉️📤

'Don't Tell the Groom' tells the story of a bride to be having second thoughts on the day of the wedding and turning to her best friend, the maid of honour, for advice. 

We're looking for 2 actresses that will display a bond of believable friendship. If you make it through auditions there'll be a round of chemistry reads to follow.

Pairs of actress friends are encouraged to email in and mention they'd like to be paired as a potential consideration for both roles. 

Looking forward to making this film. It's gonna be a good one 👰💒

This is an unpaid gig

# 🎭 **New 5-Week Dramatic Improv Course Starts Saturday! [online]**
# 
Join Theatre Momentum and improv legend Michael J Gellman** **for
**“Process: An Actor’s Journey – A Foundation for Improvised Acting”**

## Improvisation is the jazz of theatre — come play with us!

This five-week online intensive explores character, presence, and the actor’s creative process, culminating in an online performance.

## 📅 Saturdays, Oct 25 – Nov 22 · 12-3 PM Central · Via Zoom
⚡ Space is limited — reserve your spot now: 
## https://www.theatremomentum.com/guest-classes

⚡ Space is limited — reserve your spot now:

# 🎵 **Individuelle Software für Musiklehrer & Musikschulen – kostenlos entwickeln lassen!**

Hi, ich bin **Emanuel** und entwickle mit meinem Unternehmen **maßgeschneiderte Softwarelösungen** für kleine Unternehmen, Agenturen und Selbstständige – und ganz besonders für **Musiklehrer und Musikschulen**.

Ich weiß: Gerade am Anfang fehlt oft das Budget für passende Tools – deshalb **übernehme ich die Entwicklung kostenlos.**

Ob **Unterrichtsplanung, Terminbuchung, Schülerverwaltung, Stundenabrechnung oder Kursorganisation** – du bekommst eine Lösung, die wirklich zu **dir und deiner Schule** passt.

Du hast stattdessen eine **Idee für eine eigene Musik-App oder Lernplattform**? Auch super spannend – schreib mich gerne dafür an! 🎧

Ich übernehme die Entwicklung **kostenlos**, damit du **ohne Risiko starten** kannst.

Im Gegenzug kümmere ich mich (wenn du zufrieden bist) um **Hosting, Betreuung und Betrieb** – **fair, flexibel und bezahlbar.**

So entstehen **langfristige Partnerschaften**, die beiden Seiten etwas bringen.

Bei Interesse gerne PN :)

items.text:
🎬 **CASTING CALL – COVENTRY UNIVERSITY FINAL YEAR FILM** 🎬

We’re currently casting for **two main characters** in our upcoming **third-year short film project**, a **horror-comedy** shooting in **Coventry** (with the possibility of additional locations — confirmed actors will be informed in advance).

📅 **Filming Period:** Mid-February to March 2026
🎞️ **Length:** Approx. 15 minutes
🎭 **Genre:** Horror Comedy

This is an **unpaid student production**, but we will **cover travel costs and catering** during filming days.

We’re looking for **dedicated and enthusiastic actors** who are passionate about working on creative projects and open to collaborating with a student film crew.

If you’re interested, please email **davist11@coventry.ac.uk** with your **headshot, showreel (if available), and a short bio**.
Once you get in touch, I’ll send over **all the details about the audition process** and what to expect.

We’re aiming to **lock in our final cast by January**, so please make sure you’re available for the filming period mentioned above.

This is a great opportunity to gain on-set experience, expand your portfolio, and be part of a fun and ambitious student film! 🎥✨

items.text:
Hi there - I hope you are well and don’t mind me posting here.

We’re offering a unique theatre experience for someone who loves theatre to share the magic from a private opera box with a person from another generation — a grandparent & grandchild, friends, or colleagues.

This filmed project, created by The Guardian and a paid partner, celebrates the joy of theatre and the connections it inspires.

**The younger participant must be 18+.**

**All participants must be based in or around London.**

If anyone you know would like to be part of this special experience, they can email stories@rosewaite.com telling us:

Their story together

Why theatre matters to them both

Please include a phone number and photos of the two of them

Shoot dates: 24 & 25 November

Paid opportunity, £375 flat fee per person for both days

Please share this opportunity with family, friends and colleagues.

Thank you so much!

MY MOMMA’S ERA: THE MUSICAL – SEEN THROUGH MY MOTHER’S LENS

Saturday, November 8, 2025
Greenwood Oasis Theater – 7621 S. Greenwood Ave, Chicago, IL
Showtime: 7 PM | VIP Experience: 4 PM | Doors Open: 6 PM
FREE PARKING

Come dressed in your best 40s, 50s, 60s, or 70s attire!
(It’s recommended — not required — for the full experience!)

Step back in time and experience a powerful musical journey through the Great Migration, Bronzeville’s rich Black history, and the soul of World War II-era Chicago — told through acting, singing, dancing, and narration.

 Featuring unforgettable portrayals of:
Billie Holiday, Nat King Cole, Ella Fitzgerald, Dinah Washington, Cab Calloway, Etta James
Plus a moving tribute to Minnie Riperton, Chicago’s own.

A dynamic cast. Real stories. Legendary music.
This is more than entertainment — it’s edutainment.

TICKETS & GROUP BENEFITS
Group rates (10+) already discounted online
Call 773-655-3575 for Senior & Youth group discounts!

Eventbrite (Use code: MyMommasEra2025):
 https://www.eventbrite.com/e/my-mommas-era-the-musical-stage-play-tickets-1302271441939?aff=oddtdtcreator

Zeffy (No fees to us!):
 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/my-mommas-era-the-musical-stage-play

 SUPPORT THE MOVEMENT – DONATE TODAY
Dream Real Theatre Company is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit using the arts to educate, inspire, and transform.

Zeffy (tax-deductible):
https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/donate-to-make-a-difference-19332

 PayPal:
https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=4HEYR2LBTP8J8

Zelle: 773-655-3575

PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS — NOW SEEKING FINAL CREW MEMBERS

**We’re bringing a few more people aboard an already full production team for George Orwell’s *****1984*****, directed by M.A.C.**

We’re looking for:
* **Assistant Producer**
* **Social Media / Marketing** Manager
* **Sound Board Operator**
* **Lighting Board Operator**

Performances run **December 4–7, 2025** at **Three Stories Theater (937 Liberty Ave, Downtown Pittsburgh)**.

Our **cast and crew of over 30 artists** are already deep in rehearsals and production work, and our design team has fully built out the world of the show. We’re looking for a few final team members to join the effort and help bring this ambitious production to completion.

**ASSISTANT PRODUCER**

Supports the Executive Producer with logistics, communications, scheduling, and coordination across departments. Ideal for someone organized, proactive, and interested in hands-on producing experience in a professional theatre environment.

**SOCIAL MEDIA / MARKETING MANAGER**

Join our marketing team to help manage social channels, coordinate content posting, and support our show rollout.
We already have **two resident photographers/videographers** and a **backlog of content ready to be edited, polished, and posted**. You’ll be shaping how this production is presented to the public.

SOUND & LIGHTING BOARD OPERATORS

We have professional **sound and lighting designers** who have already built out the show’s systems and cues — we’re simply looking for **two operators** to put that design work into action during **tech week and performances**.
Experience with QLab (for Sound) or ETC lighting consoles (for Lighting) is helpful, but a good sense of focus and teamwork is most important.

**COMPENSATION TYPE:** Volunteer / Possible post-show stipend
*(We want to be transparent: these are volunteer positions, but if funds allow, a small stipend may be available after the production.) *

**DATES & COMMITMENTS:**
* **Rehearsals (for reference):** Sundays, 6–9 PM starting August 3, 2025
Trust Arts Education Center — 807 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Tech Week:** November 24 – December 3, 2025 (dark day on Thanksgiving)
* **Performances:** December 4–7, 2025 (5 performances total)
Three Stories Theater — 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA

We’re happy to work with your schedule — please share any known conflicts when reaching out.

**TO APPLY**
Please email **playboxpgh@gmail.com** with:
* Resume (or a brief note on your experience and interest)
* Availability during tech week and performances

If it seems like a good fit, we’ll be in touch right away!

Thank you,
Marc Palombo
**PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS**

*wiek: 25–50 lat*

***azjatycki typ urody***

# 📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na e-mail:
# **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

**🎥 Kamila Boichenko**

Male, 25-30 years old, speaking any other language than Polish/Russian/Ukrainian.
We have no preferences regarding appearance 🙂

Please send a private message, including a demo 😁

Nonprofit offer!

items.text:
MERIVENTS is Hiring!

We’re excited to assemble our Dream Team of talented professionals for iconic NYC events like SNL wrap parties, movie premieres, and sporting events.

**Building Our Dream Team**

At Amerivents, we are committed to assembling and empowering a "Dream Team" of talented individuals who bring diverse skills, shared values, and a unified purpose to every endeavor. Much like a championship sports team, we believe that our collective success is built on the strength and collaboration of our team members, each contributing their unique expertise to achieve exceptional results.

**Now Hiring FRONT OF HOUSE:**
* Catering Hospitality Staff
* Servers
* Bartenders
* Captains

**Now Hiring BACK OF HOUSE:**
* Dishwasher
* Utility
* Grill Cook
* Line Cook

**Requirements:**

2+ years of catering or high-end retail experience

You must be 18 or older

**Next Steps:**
1. Complete the interview survey here: [https://forms.gle/r3B2ib3kssxRfF5v8](https://forms.gle/r3B2ib3kssxRfF5v8)
2. Visit[ www.amerivents.com](http://www.amerivents.com/) and click “Apply” (mention “CORE-NYC” in the referral box).

**Why Amerivents?**
* Fast-paced, exciting, and team-oriented work environment
* Flexible schedules—you choose your availability!
* Gain unforgettable experiences in the hospitality industry
* Experience unique and inspiring event locations!

**What We’re Looking For:**
* 2+ years of catering or high-end retail experience
* Professional, adaptable, and radiate positivity team players
* Composure under pressure and ability to adapt to dynamic environments
* Flexible and reliable team players who can seamlessly adjust to varying roles and tasks
* Ability to lift 50 lbs and stand for extended periods

**To Our Team:**
We offer the chance to pursue your passions while contributing to a company that values your unique talents and provides the support you need to excel.

We look forward to hearing from you!

**This is not an official job offer**

Angela Boehm Casting is now casting talent for a TV Pilot "The Land"! 

We are thrilled to announce a TV Pilot coming to Cleveland. We are looking for EXTRAS, TRAINED DRIVERS, STAND INS , and DOUBLES. This shoot will be split from middle of the afternoon till the middle of the night. (Times to be determined) 
This project will be taking place in the Cleveland, OH area ! 

Please read carefully below for details! 
DETAILS: 
Project: TV Pilot "The Land" Filming 
Location: Cleveland, OH area (MUST BE LOCAL) 

Shoot Date(s): November 15th, 2025 - More dates coming in the new year 
Background Rate: $120/8hr 
Trained Drivers: $120/8hr + $150 bump 
Stand In: $128/8hr Double: $136/8hr 

Link to submit: http://bit.ly/3Lki3Bb

Kind regards, Angela Boehm Casting Team 

PLEASE NOTE: This is just a submission. If you are booked, we will reach out to YOU.

items.text:
🎬 Hey zusammen!

Ich bin David, 55 Jahre alt aus Frankfurt am Main.
Ich bin 1,80 m groß, sportlich gebaut und vom Typ her eher südländisch & modern.

Ich habe zwar noch keine Filmerfahrung, aber richtig Lust, vor der Kamera zu stehen und in verschiedene Rollen zu schlüpfen – ob als Statist, Kleindarsteller oder für kleinere Szenen.

Ich bin zuverlässig, offen und bringe gute Laune mit 😊
Wenn jemand ein Casting in Frankfurt oder Umgebung anbietet oder Statisten sucht, freue ich mich sehr über eine Nachricht!

📧 Kontakt: teppichzentrum14@gmail.com

Liebe Grüße
Dieter

At VRASP, we support actors at every stage of their journey. This scene is from our Elevate Class. Actors @mcractressemmaturner and @scriptedthebest - This is the quality of work taking place in Elevate.

Whether you’re just starting out or already booking roles, our classes provide a professional yet supportive space where you can truly develop.

VRASP is Hampshire’s number one drop-in acting class for a reason. By attending, you gain access to expert coaching, on-camera training, personalised feedback, networking opportunities, and real industry insight.

Come and experience VRASP - where real actors see real results.

Do you have a passion for all things scary?

A walk that sends shivers down spines?

Or maybe you just love being part of the chaos behind the scares?

Fear Columbus in Columbus, Ohio  is HIRING IMMEDIATELY for:

🩸 Haunted House Actors (unleash your inner monster, clown, or demon)

🩸 Event Staff (keep the terror running smoothly from the shadows)

✨ No experience? No problem. We’ll train you to scare like a pro.

✨ evening shifts + the most fun job you’ll ever have.

✨ Be part of one of the largest haunted attractions in Ohio.

This is your chance to join our spooky family and create memories (and nightmares) that guests won’t forget!

💀 Apply NOW and come be a part of all the spooky fun! 

⚡ Don’t wait — the screams start soon and spots are filling FAST! 

Click the link below or in my bio for info on what it entails working here and for the application! 

Can't wait to see you <3

[https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/](https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/)

Hey everyone!

I’m Ryan, a Casting Producer for Family Feud Canada.

Family Feud Canada is currently casting and I’m looking for families from **BRITISH COLUMBIA!** Those who make it onto the show will have a chance to win up to $30,000!

To apply or get more info you can check out the link on the attached poster, go on CBC’s website, or by searching “apply for Family Feud Canada” online.

When you apply, select “Casting Associate Ryan” when it asks how you heard about applying. This way I’ll be able to fast track your family through the audition process.

If you have any questions, feel free to send me an email or check out the FAQ’s on our website.

All the best, and happy feuding!

Ryan Savein
Associate Casting Producer | Family Feud Canada
rsavein@zone3.ca

Wygląd: Sympatyczna młoda kobieta o regularnych rysach twarzy. Średniego wzrostu. Zawsze schludnie ubrana, styl bliżej oficjalnego ze względu na wykonywany zawód.

Szczegóły: We wszystkim stara się kierować sprawiedliwością.

**3.Agnieszka Prudniak (19 lat) **– studentka.

Szczegóły: Podatna na wpływ opinii znajomych, jak większość nastolatków. Maksymalistka – widzi świat w czerni i bieli.

Sceny: 3, 6, 18, 21, 22, 22A, 23, 23A  **TERMIN 28-29.10**

Sceny: 2, 5, 8, 22, 22A  **TERMIN 28.10**

📢 Szukamy statystów do nagrań w 5 gwiazdkowym hotelu!

Chcesz wziąć udział w profesjonalnych nagraniach promujących  hotel, restaurację Vanilla Sky i Vanilla Spa? 🎥

🎬 Kogo szukamy:

rodzin (najlepiej z dziećmi) – do roli w pakiecie rodzinnym

par – do ujęć w ramach pakietu romantycznego

grup przyjaciół – do materiałów o pobycie z przyjaciółmi

właścicieli psów 🐶 – do ujęć o pobycie z pupilem

📍 Miejsce nagrań: Niebieski Art Hotel & Spa, ul. Flisacka 3, Kraków

🕓 Czas nagrań: ok. 2–3 godziny

📅 Data: do ustalenia indywidualnego

💙 Wynagrodzenie barterowe:

voucher na 4-daniową kolację w restauracji Vanilla Sky dla każdej osoby biorącej udział w nagraniu 🍽️

Zgłoszenia (imię, nazwisko, kilka zdań o sobie i zdjęcie) prosimy wysyłać na adres: emsocialagency@gmail.com lub w wiadomości prywatnej. 

#szukamystatystów #nagraniakraków #wynagrodzeniebarterowe

items.text:
# **🎬 CASTING – aktor mężczyzna (azjatycki typ urody)**

**Ekipa Activity Area**, zdobywcy 2 miejsca **w konkursie 48 Hour Film Project Poland 2025**, dzięki czemu zakwalifikowani do prestiżowego konkursu **YesWeCannes**, poszukuje:

***👤 Aktor – mężczyzna***

*wiek: 25–50 lat*

***azjatycki typ urody***

*dobra znajomość języka polskiego*

*doświadczenie aktorskie mile widziane, ale nie jest wymagane*

🎥** Termin zdjęć:** 14–17 listopada 2025

📍 **Miejsce:** Warszawa

Projekt realizowany w ramach **konkursu YesWeCannes**, z **profesjonalną ekipą nagrodzoną w 48 Hour Film Project Poland.**

# 📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na e-mail:
# **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

W treści zgłoszenia prosimy podać:

*1. Imię i nazwisko*

*2. Miejsce zamieszkania*

*3. Zdjęcia (portret i sylwetka)*

*4. Showreel i/lub portfolio*

*5. Wzrost oraz wymiary*

*6. Dane do kontaktu: nr. telefonu oraz email*

Czekam na zgłoszenia i serdecznie pozdrawiam,

**🎥 Kamila Boichenko**

**Reżyserka obsady**

✨CASTING IS LIVE! ✨

Between Acts is looking for singers in the North-West to audition for our first ever cabaret evening! 

The theme is 'Miscast' so it will be songs paired with unlikely people. We ask that you fill out our audition form (found in the link below), send in a 2 minute self tape and the deadline to apply is the 9th of November.

All the information is here and we'll be releasing an FAQ video soon to answer some more questions but, if you do have any questions, follow the contact info or our link-tree below!

Break a leg!🎭

https://linktr.ee/Betweenacts_?utm_source=linktree_profile_share&ltsid=ebce1e20-f8b8-4d1a-8689-b6770d970b26

items.text:
MODEL NEEDED FOR SHOOT IN CHESTER 📍
 
We are looking for 1 model for a restaurant photoshoot in Chester on Wednesday 8th October. The photos and videos will be used on the restaurants’ website & social media to showcase the experience of the venue.

Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot:
 
📆 Date: Wednesday 8th October. 
⏰ Time: 12pm-4pm
 
Requirements:
 
-       Age: Between 21-30
-       Female
-       Wearing casual outfit. 
- some playful tiktoks will also be filmed, so you must be comfortable with playful /sassy content (e.g like this: https://www.instagram.com/reel/DI4rOAITfbP/?igsh=MXd6cXFyaWtqdDdpMg==
 
💸 Compensation:
-       We have the budget to offer each model £125 for the few hours. 
- Food & drinks will be provided. 
 
More in-depth briefing will be given to those selected.
 
Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot and we will be in touch via Facebook DMs.

✨ A pilláid megérdemlik a ragyogást az ünnepekre is ✨

Sok szeretettel várlak a XI. kerületben, a Fehérvári út 168–178/A alatt (1116 Budapest), ahol gyönyörű, tartós és személyre szabott pillákkal varázsolom még különlegesebbé a megjelenésed 😊🫵

🎄 A karácsonyi időszak közeledik, és a helyek rohamosan fogynak, úgyhogy ha szeretnél tökéletes pillákat az ünnepekre, ne hagyd az utolsó percre a foglalást!

💌 Időpontért írj üzenetet, és gondoskodjunk együtt arról, hogy csillogj az ünnepek alatt is 💫

Munkáim/árlista:

Poszukuję Hosta Cosplay'owego na Targi PGA! Warszawa - Poznań

**Poszukuję:** Mężczyzny o ciemnej karnacji, rozmiar ubrania: XS/S, szczupła budowa ciała i wzrost w okolicy 165. spodnie w stroju mają w talii 85cm, a opaska na przedramię 24 w obwodzie. strój zawiera włosy i skarpetki w kolorze

**Termin: 24.10 - 26.10 (PGA):** Oferujemy transport z Warszawy i z powrotem, nocleg, wyżywienie we własnym zakresie.

Praca po 12h dziennie w tym przerwa na posiłek i toaletę, nie trzeba nic mówić - wystarczy chodzić w stroju.

**Termin 2 (obowiązkowe oba):** 03.11 (Warszawa) - zdjęcia studyjne, dodatkowo płatne 400zł (4-6h)

**Rozliczenie:** do tygodnia po 03.11

**Płatność:** 24.10 - 26.10 -> 2000zł , 03.11 -> 400zł

Proszę o zgłoszenia osób dyspozycyjnych w obu terminach i spełniających powyższe warunki.

Zgłoszenia wysyłacie na: **karina.szymocha@gmail.com**, w tytule: **HOST PGA**

W treści:

- Imię i nazwisko

- wiek

- wymiary ubrań

- nr tel do kontaktu 

- 2 aktualne zdjęcia twarzy i sylwetki

Na maile czekam do najbliższego Poniedziałku. Skontaktuję się z wybranymi osobami.

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – VHELMA SUE (Poster Below)**

*A 3Wize Media Short Film (12th Episode of “The 13th Episode” Anthology)*

**Union Status:** SAG-AFTRA Micro-Budget Agreement
**Location:** Colorado Springs/Denver/Pueblo, CO
**Production Type:** Short Film
**Genre:** Psychological Mystery / Supernatural Thriller
**Filming Dates:** Nov/Dec
**Compensation:** IMDB credit, meals, festival submissions, and portfolio-building opportunity
**Distribution:** This project will be submitted to multiple film festivals as part of *The 13th Episode* anthology series. 

ABOUT THE PROJECT

***VHELMA SUE*** is a short film in *The 13th Episode* Anthology Series. It follows Detective Vhelma Sue and her partner as they struggle with inner conflict while investigating a mysterious pattern of deaths linked to an unsolved childhood case. Set mostly inside a vehicle, the story unfolds through intimate dialogue, theological questions, and layered character dynamics. It connects to other award-winning films in the anthology, including *Fare Share*, *Checkmate*, and *Doc Feel Good*, forming part of a growing cinematic universe.

This is a professional but collaborative learning environment. We are open to talent at all stages of their careers, especially those looking to build IMDb credits, gain experience working under a SAG-AFTRA Micro-Budget Agreement, and collaborate with award-winning filmmakers and talent.
> 

***Note: This SAG-AFTRA Micro-Budget project cannot be used toward SAG eligibility or to gain SAG affiliation.***

SEEKING THE FOLLOWING ROLES

**(LEAD) VHELMA SUE – Female, 30s-40s, open ethnicity**
Confident, witty, layered. Southern-born detective with a quiet past and private motivations*.**** (BONUS...not required***...***IF YOU CAN PULL OFF A SOUTHERN *****ACCENT***** AND THE LOOK IN THE POSTER!!)***

**(SUPPORTING) DETECTIVE BRYANT – Male or Female, 30s–50s, any ethnicity**
Quick-thinking, professional. Appears in one short confirmation scene and again during an investigation. Must handle concise, convincing detective dialogue with presence.

**(SUPPORTING) DETECTIVE HERNANDEZ – Male or Female, 30s–50s, any ethnicity**
Sharp, focused. Appears in limited screen time during an investigative sequence. Strong energy and realism preferred.

**(FEATURED) BODY OF MYA – Female, early 20's - 30's, any ethnicity**
Portrays the body of a young woman discovered in a key scene. No lines. Must be comfortable lying still for extended takes, possibly with light FX makeup.

**(BACKGROUND EXTRAS)** – 5 Roles Available Adults of various ages/ethnicities to appear in background scenes at police precinct, crime scene, and coffee shop. No dialogue, just naturalistic presence. Helpful for early-career actors looking to gain experience.

**SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS**

Please send the following to (or have agent send to)  **casting@3wizemedia.com** 

Headshot (professional or clear recent photo...does NOT have to be a professional photo if no H/S is available) 

Resume or reel (if available) 

City you are based in 

Role(s) you are submitting for

Availability for NOV/DEC 

Subject line: **VHELMA SUE – [Role Name] Submission** 

NOTES This production operates under the **SAG-AFTRA Micro-Budget Agreement**. All selected talent will receive: FUN...IMDB credit On-set meals Copy of final film, festival promotion information via festival submissions, and professional experience with an award winning multi-film anthology project.

items.text:
Hey filmy friends!!!

Community is a lot like a garden. If you want a healthy, vibrant one, you gotta cultivate that shit. You gotta tend it and care for it. So, let's really dig in and build the most incredible community/garden we possibly can. 

This means ya gotta get off your tuchas and show up. Show up for events and meetings and elections and programs and festivals and screenings and all the hooooo ha. 

You want people to come see your project, ya gotta go see theirs. 
You want people to hire you, ya gotta get out and meet the people hiring. 
You want to find great people to be on your set, then ya gotta get out and meet the people you want to hire. 

Get involved!!! Sign up for shit!! Have fun!!! Make cool stuff!!! 

The next fun thing we have is this Friday. The CFVA is hosting a Halloween party. You can dress up or not, but be there! Show up. Play. Engage. Connect. It's how we will grow CO Film into something undeniable!!!! 

Come find me and say hi. I'll be busting ghosts!

Hello Everyone!

My name is Rayonna Price and I am writer/director for a short film called 'Cursed'. It is a University of Colorado Denver film.

A woman suffers through a rough day, will she get through unscathed or will someone lose their head?

Dionne and Jason have been casted for, however, we still are still looking for our Nadine and Bryce. All locations are in central Denver, and our filming dates are November 13th-16th. Transportation can be provided.

To audition and find sides follow the google link here: https://forms.gle/KJJKmE3bG3HgYHkDA

Actors will be reimbursed, please audition we would love to have you apart of production!

Thank you!

My name is Rayonna Price and I am writer/director for a short film called 'Cursed'. It is a University of Colorado Denver film.

A woman suffers through a rough day, will she get through unscathed or will someone lose their head?

Dionne and Jason have been casted for, however, we still are still looking for our Nadine and Bryce. All locations are in central Denver, and our filming dates are November 13th-16th. Transportation can be provided.

Actors will be reimbursed, please audition we would love to have you apart of production!

Thank you!

items.text:
Für meinen kommenden Kurzfilm „Zwischen Licht und Schatten“ (Drehort gebe ich noch bekannt) am 10.01 und 11.01 suche ich noch engagierte Mitwirkende:

🎬 Regie

Ich suche eine/n Regisseur:in, die/der Lust hat, gemeinsam mit mir diesen emotional intensiven Kurzfilm umzusetzen. Das Projekt ist charaktergetrieben und bewegt sich zwischen innerem Konflikt, familiärer Bindung und Selbstfindung.

Erfahrung ist wünschenswert, aber kein Muss — wichtiger ist Leidenschaft, Teamgeist und Gespür für authentisches Schauspiel.

🎭 Rollen

👩‍🦰 Lucy (ca. 25–28 Jahre)

– Stellas beste Freundin

– herzlich, empathisch, gute Zuhörerin

– ruhig, aber präsent, gibt Stella Halt

– Spielalter: ca. 26 Jahre

– Drehtage: [1–2]

– Keine Gage, aber Verpflegung + Material für Showreel

👦 Felix (Spielalter 20-22 Jahre)

– Stellas jüngerer Bruder

– ehemals drogenabhängig, heute sehr zurückhaltend, manchmal verschlossen

– steht im Zwiespalt zwischen Angst und Stärke

– hat Respekt vor Viktor (dem Bösewicht , drogendealer), aber kann sich im entscheidenden Moment behaupten

– Drehtage: 10.01-11.01

Kurzinhalt

Die 25-jährige Stella lebt zurückgezogen, misstrauisch gegenüber Männern und misstrauisch

gegenüber Gefühlen. Als sie im Park den sportlichen, offenen Nick kennenlernt, entsteht eine

leise Nähe – doch Stella blockt jeden Annäherungsversuch ab.

Während sie langsam Vertrauen zu Nick fasst, gerät ihr Bruder Felix in ernste Schwierigkeiten:

Er schuldet Victor, einem gefährlichen Drogendealer, 5.000 Euro. Victor bedroht Felix und sucht

schließlich auch Stella auf, um an sein Geld zu kommen.

Eines Abends eskaliert die Situation. Victor lauert Stella auf – und als Nick hinzukommt, versucht

er, sie zu schützen. Er hält ihm sein Portemonnaie mit 300 Euro hin, um Zeit zu gewinnen. Doch

Victor wird wütend: „Ich will mein Geld – oder einer von euch stirbt!“

Nick sagt zu Stella, sie solle laufen. Zitternd flieht sie und versteckt sich hinter einem Baum.

Dann kommt es zum Kampf zwischen Nick und Victor. In einem verzweifelten Moment wird

Victor im Bauch verletzt und bricht zusammen. Als Stille einkehrt, tritt Stella hervor, ruft „Nick!“,

läuft zu ihm, und beide fallen sich unter Tränen in die Arme. Ein Moment zwischen Dunkelheit

und Hoffnung – und vielleicht der Beginn einer echten Heilung.

Drehtort noch unbekannt Max im Umkreis von 200 km  von Nordhorn

🗓️ Drehzeitraum: Januar 2026

💬  – gern per PN oder E-Mail an [de.pascalis1990@web.de] kontaktieren

We’re looking for a passionate and creative teacher to join our After-School Musical Theatre Program based at a local elementary school in Pasadena.

 • Schedule: Once a week, 1-hour class

 • Students: Kindergarten & 1st Grade

 • Goal: Prepare a short performance for families and fellow students in April

 • Focus areas: Creativity, focus, teamwork, confident stage presence, basic choreography, and simple songs

 • Compensation: $70 per class

 • Start date: ASAP

✨ Experience working with young children is a must!

🎭 Please send your resume/portfolio and contact info — I’d love to connect!

📩 Direct message me or feel free to email me at em@bigstepsla.com

📱You can also reach out via Instagram @bigstepsla

Looking forward to hearing from you!

items.text:
** CASTING CALL: Are You Ready to Get **Disconnected? PAID

We’re looking for **real people** — not actors — to take part in a six-week challenge:
 👉 Cut nonessential media use
 👉 Reclaim your time
 👉 Pursue a goal or dream you’ve been putting off

This is your chance to find out what life looks like when you step away from the screen and step into your purpose.

💭 Maybe you’ll learn a new language.
 🎸 Write a song.
 🪵 Build something.
 💬 Reconnect with someone you love.

We’ll follow your journey as part of a hopeful, cinematic documentary about using technology **intentionally** — not compulsively.

📅 **Filming:** 6-week period
 📍 **Location:** Anywhere in the US

✨ **To Apply:**
 

1️⃣ **Record:** Film your 3–5 minute audition video in a well-lit space, speaking clearly and authentically.

2️⃣ **Upload:** Upload it as a private or unlisted link (YouTube, Vimeo, or Google Drive).

3️⃣ **Apply:** Complete the official application form and paste your video link when prompted.

Click the link for more information and to apply:

[https://thegoodandthebeautiful.bamboohr.com/careers/100](https://thegoodandthebeautiful.bamboohr.com/careers/100)

items.title: (no title)

items.text:
🎬 Short Film “ Glasses” (London)

Hi everyone,

I’m Anil an independent filmmaker currently working on a short film titled “Glasses” — a heartfelt story about an encounter between two strangers.

🎥 Shoot: 1–2 days in London (2nd or 3rd week of Nov 2025)

💰 Type: Independent short - paid, with credits, meals, and footage for reel - details will be shared and discussed once shortlisted.

Casting:

1️⃣ Male (25–35) – expressive, natural, grounded.

2️⃣ Male (60–70) – warm, witty, emotionally subtle.

If interested, please send a short self-tape / intro video and your availability to:

📧 angopproduction@gmail.com

I’m happy to share the script and concept note with shortlisted actors.

#CastingCall #ShortFilm #LondonFilm #ActorSearch #MyGlasses

topComments.text: Fee, please? Asking for a friend.  Thanks

items.text:
🎭 TONIGHT: Queer Play Reading Club with special guest Jennifer Lunn
📍 The Railway, Clapham
📅 Tuesday 21 October | 7pm–11pm

Join the Queer Theatre community tonight for an evening of queer storytelling and new writing.

We’ll be reading Es & Flo by Jennifer Lunn, an award-winning play about love, memory and the life two women built together behind closed doors — coloured with memories of the Greenham Common Women’s Peace Camp, celebrating solidarity, courage and the power of chosen family. Jennifer Lunn will be joining us in person for a Q&A about her work and process.

The evening also features new writing from David Wattees, Freddie Haberfellner, and Grace Statton, giving writers and actors the chance to share work, connect and grow together in a supportive, queer-led space.

🕡 Arrivals from 6:30pm (tea, coffee & snacks)
🎭 Reading 7pm–10:30pm | Drinks & socialising after

Be part of a growing network of LGBTQIA+ artists — join us each month as we read, create and collaborate across all Queer Theatre projects.

items.text:
**Fortgeschrittene Method-Acting-Kurse **🎭

**In Berlin & Online weltweit | Auf Deutsch & Englisch** 

Ich bin eine international arbeitende Schauspielerin, Drehbuchautorin und Schauspielcoach mit abgeschlossenem Schauspielstudium und langjähriger Erfahrung auf Bühne und vor der Kamera.

Meine Arbeit basiert auf einer fortgeschrittenen Method-Acting-Technik, entwickelt in enger Zusammenarbeit mit dem Regisseur Robert Castle (International Theatre New York) und der weltbekannten Hollywood-Coachin Susan Batson.

🎭**Mein Ansatz**

Basierend auf der Arbeit von Stanislavski, Lee Strasberg, Stella Adler und weiterentwickelt durch Robert Castle, ermögliche ich Schauspieler*innen:

•Emotionale Wahrheit durch sense memory Übungen

•Figuren von innen heraus lebendig zu machen

•Spontan, ehrlich und im Moment zu spielen

•Emotional frei und künstlerisch kreativ zu arbeiten – auf Bühne &
 Leinwand 

Dies ist kein Grundlagenkurs, sondern eine tiefgehende, künstlerisch fordernde Methode für Schauspieler*innen, die ihr Handwerk auf ein neues Level bringen möchten.

💡**Was du erwarten kannst**

•Intensive Vorbereitung auf Vorsprechen (Theater, Film,
 Schauspielschulen)

•Rollenarbeit für Bühne und Film

•Arbeit an Monologen & Szenen (z. B. Shakespeare, Pinter,  

 Williams, Churchill, Berg, Sartre u. a.)

•Kamera- und Self-Tape-Training

•Stimm-, Sprech- & Körperarbeit

•Individuelles Coaching zur künstlerischen Entwicklung

•Insiderwissen: Agenturen, Netzwerken & Berufsrealität

🎓E**rfolge meiner Schüler*innen**

✔️Aufnahme an renommierten Schauspielschulen wie Ernst Busch
     Berlin oder der HKB Bern

✔️Besetzungen in Film- und Serienproduktionen

✔️Künstlerische und emotionale Weiterentwicklung durch präzise,
     individuelle Arbeit

Als zertifizierter Life Coach begleite ich Schauspieler*innen zusätzlich in kreativen Prozessen und bei persönlichen Herausforderungen.

Kontakt: coaching@isabelle-mann.com

[https://www.isabelle-mann.com/de/coaching.htm](https://www.isabelle-mann.com/de/coaching.htm)

topComments.text: Was kostet es ? Würde den Kurs gerne jemanden schenken - kennt sich gut mit der Strasberg Methode aus!

items.text:
Hi 

We're looking for 11–14-year-olds across the UK to star in an Education series, My Life, My Religion. 

This exciting project, produced by CTVC will showcase the lives of young people from different faiths and worldviews. The films will be used by schools nationwide to help children learn about religion, culture and identity in a fun, friendly and inspiring way.

We want to hear from young people who are:
* ﻿﻿Proud to share their religion or worldview (Muslim, Jewish, Buddhist, Humanist, or others).
* ﻿﻿Confident and curious, with lots of energy and personality.
* ﻿﻿Supported by a parent or guardian who is happy for them to take part.

Filming will take place in 2025/early 2026 across the UK. This is a paid opportunity, and all travel/expenses will be covered. We follow strict BBC safeguarding policies.

How to apply:

Parents/guardians should email *casting@ctvc.co.uk* with:
* ﻿﻿The young person's name, age, and location
* ﻿﻿A short paragraph about their faith/worldview and why they'd like to take part

Please pass this opportunity on to anyone who you think will be interested in taking part. 

Best wishes,

Sam

items.text:
# (Paid) Casting for George Fox University Student Film, (Hillsboro, Oregon)

We are a group of George Fox students shooting a short film at the Airplane Home for our Location Production class, looking for a total of three non-union actors.

Project Title: Clearing The Air

Location: Airplane Home: 15270 SW Holly Hill Rd, Hillsboro, OR 97123

Safety Considerations: Dress for potential rain and cold weather. Several cats roam around the area, so be weary if you have any allergies. The actor that plays Jean will hold a non functional prop firearm.

 Shoot Dates: 10/28/2025 and 10/30/2025, 2:00PM - 9:00PM

Age Requirement: 18 and over

Pay: 50$ per day

You will receive a collection of your scenes to include in your reel.

Synopsis: Lost in the woods, siblings Gertie and Hudson come upon an airplane containing valuables. The sister aims to ransack the plane, while her brother urges her against it. Upon the return of the airplane’s resident, Jean, the sister attempts to escape with her spoils by attacking Jean from behind while her brother serves as a distraction. Her plan is thwarted by Jean, who catches her in the act, and Hudson, who reveals her presence and forces her to return what she stole. Once the two parties agree to part ways, it is revealed that Jean is a fugitive with a reward for her capture, worth more than anything the siblings could’ve stolen.

Character Breakdown

(Antagonist) Jean: A perceptive older woman with a soft face but a hardened demeanor, a criminal past, and a lifetime of secrets behind her eyes.

Age: The character is meant to be in her early sixties, but her age isn't a strict guideline.

(Protagonist) Hudson: A thoughtful late teen with dark hair, an anxious posture, and a subdued retro rock styling, who has a tendency to let others walk over him.

He is the younger brother to Gertie.

"Think William Miller in Almost Famous but more frazzled and sarcastic."

Age: Roughly 18-19

(Protagonist) Gertie: An outdoorsy, has-it-all-together college girl with a “Karen Carpenter” fashion sense, a hidden impulsive nature, and a proclivity toward not seeing beyond her own scope.

Age: Around 20-21 years old

Audition sides are in the link below. Please record your auditions and send them to Bronson Revilla at brevilla21@georgefox.edu.

[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing)

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – Gaunt Man / Doctor (Dual Role) in Short Film *****The Damned Spot***

**Production Title:** *The Damned Spot*
**Company:** SWRCO Studios / Racetothefinishline Studios
**Location:** Atlanta, GA
**Union Status:** Non-Union
**Compensation:** $200 flat rate (2 half-days)
**Role: Gaunt Man / Doctor (Male, 40s–80s)**

**Character Description:**
This is a dual-performance role. The **Doctor** appears grounded, calm, and professional — a clinician trying to reassure his patient. The **Gaunt Man** is his nightmarish double: unsettling, skeletal in presence, and haunting. The shift between the two is central to the film’s psychological horror.

**Requirements:**
* Male, age range 40–85
* Ability to portray both a grounded, realistic character and a chilling, silent presence
* Strong facial expression and physical control — much of the horror relies on stillness and presence
* Comfortable with light makeup (pale complexion, under-eye work) and basic VFX markers
**Filming Commitment:**
* 2 Half-Days
* $200 flat rate
**To Apply:**

Please submit:
* Headshot and resume (or reel, if available)
* Brief note about prior experience in psychological drama or horror
* Contact information

Send submissions to: **studio@swrco.us**
**Deadline:** **10-24-2025**

🎬 **CASTING CALL – COVENTRY UNIVERSITY FINAL YEAR FILM** 🎬

We’re currently casting for **two main characters** in our upcoming **third-year short film project**, a **horror-comedy** shooting in **Coventry** (with the possibility of additional locations — confirmed actors will be informed in advance).

📅 **Filming Period:** Mid-February to March 2026
🎞️ **Length:** Approx. 15 minutes
🎭 **Genre:** Horror Comedy

This is an **unpaid student production**, but we will **cover travel costs and catering** during filming days.

We’re looking for **dedicated and enthusiastic actors** who are passionate about working on creative projects and open to collaborating with a student film crew.

If you’re interested, please email **davist11@coventry.ac.uk** with your **headshot, showreel (if available), and a short bio**.
Once you get in touch, I’ll send over **all the details about the audition process** and what to expect.

We’re aiming to **lock in our final cast by January**, so please make sure you’re available for the filming period mentioned above.

This is a great opportunity to gain on-set experience, expand your portfolio, and be part of a fun and ambitious student film! 🎥✨

👋Hi Everyone! I'm Ash, a movement practitioner and professional stage and film Actress with a BFA and an MA in Acting, and over 7 years experience teaching/producing. 

🍂I have 5 SPOTS LEFT at my **Art of Letting Go** workshop THIS SATURDAY! This is a 3-hour acting + movement workshop that helps you release the tension you’ve been carrying- in your craft, your body, and your life.

👉You do not need to be an artist to participate. If you’ve been feeling stuck, disconnected, or just ready for a reset… this is for you! It will be fun and transformative, I promise :)

💚DM me or Scan the code below, to book!

items.text:
📣🎬 CASTING CALL - Short Period Drama 

We are casting for The Stuntman, a 3-minute period drama made as part of our final year at UWE Bristol. The film will be shot in Bristol in the week commencing 10th November 2025 (exact dates TBC). This is a student project, unpaid, but with expenses covered. The film is intended for university showcase and festival submission.

Story:
Set in 1920s Wiltshire, The Stuntman follows Ed Morris, a small-town silent cinema owner fighting to keep his theatre alive as the arrival of sound threatens to change film forever. With his fiancée Alice by his side, Ed stages one last ambitious stunt in the hope of saving his cinema - and their livelihood. A warm yet bittersweet drama about determination, passion and the march of technological change.

Roles:
Ed Morris (Lead, 28)
Charming, intelligent, and hardworking. Outwardly confident, but hiding a quiet desperation as he struggles to keep silent film alive. Needs strong screen presence and subtle emotional depth.

Alice Fardon (Lead, 22–23)
Ed’s fiancée. Feisty, loyal, and practical. She supports his dreams but occasionally shows frustration at his all-consuming determination.

Community Extras
Townsfolk gathering to watch Ed’s big stunt. A mix of ages. Families, workers and individuals. To capture the atmosphere of a 1920s local community.

Apply by: 1st November 2025
To Apply: Please send a headshot, CV (or Spotlight/Mandy link), and any showreel/self-tape to: Scarlet2.Gerry@live.uwe.ac.uk

Please include in email subject: THE STUNTMAN & NAME

message.text: Immer wieder stehen für  einige mir bekannten, befreundeten Musiker und Kunst schaffenden plötzlich  die kreativen Zeiger still. Idole und Künstler unserer Jugend, gehören auf einmal zur Geschichte. Mit Wolke7 habe ich für mich einen Weg gefunden, meine Trauer über diese Verluste, der fehlenden  Menschen, zu bewältigen. Wenn ich damit auch anderen diesen schönen Gedanken vermitteln kann, ist es doch ok.

topComments.text:
Check out some of the agency sites and look at the photos, most want straightforward headshots, half body, or full shots . As already said these are too dark and they’re staged. 
A casting director is likely just to scroll past them. 
Good luck
Your pictures are incredibly dark - it seems obvious but the main advice that leaps out at me would be to get pictures where you can be seen clearly - no-one will cast you if they can’t see you!

Hi there - I hope you are well and don’t mind me posting here.

We’re offering a unique theatre experience for someone who loves theatre to share the magic from a private opera box with a person from another generation — a grandparent & grandchild, friends, or colleagues.

This filmed project, created by The Guardian and a paid partner, celebrates the joy of theatre and the connections it inspires.

**The younger participant must be 18+.**

**All participants must be based in or around London.**

If anyone you know would like to be part of this special experience, they can email stories@rosewaite.com telling us:

Their story together

Why theatre matters to them both

Please include a phone number and photos of the two of them

Shoot dates: 24 & 25 November

Paid opportunity, £375 flat fee per person for both days

Please share this opportunity with family, friends and colleagues.

Thank you so much!

Hello everyone,

My name is Kayuran and I’m currently working on my first short mobile horror film. The script is in progress, and I’m looking for passionate people who would like to join me on this creative journey.

I’m specifically looking for:
🎬 A professional film editor
🎥 A camera operator (based in Durban/Chatsworth area)

The goal is to work together as a team and create something special. This project isn’t about making money — it’s about sharing stories and giving audiences an enjoyable and memorable film experience.

If you’re interested in being part of this project or know someone who might be, please feel free to reach out. Let’s build something amazing together!

From 
KM PICTURE

If you’re interested in being part of this project or know someone who might be, please feel free to reach out. Let’s build something amazing together!

From 
KM PICTURE

items.text:
The new Online Casting Room is here—and we’re offering something special to the first people to try it out!

The Online Casting Room simplifies and streamlines the casting process by moving it online. It’s an exclusively Canadian service that filmmakers and casting directors can use to build the cast of their dreams, and that actors can use to find their next role. Whether you’re emerging or established film talent, the Online Casting Room is here to save you time, money, and energy while extending your reach beyond your geographic location.

All you need to do to create a casting call is fill in a few quick prompts. Then, the choice to host live auditions or review self-tapes is yours. Built-in collaborative features mean your entire casting team can be involved in the process, enabling you to share notes, provide feedback, and exchange messages—all within our platform!

Our Special Offer: While right now, all access to cinewoo is free, we will be rolling out paid subscription tiers in the next future. To thank the early supporters of the Online Casting Room, we’re offering an extended 2-year free access period to our platform to everybody who posts a casting call between now and December 31, 2025 (effective when paid subscriptions are introduced). 

You have everything to gain, and nothing to lose—step into the Online Casting Room at [www.cinewoo.com](http://www.cinewoo.com) today!

items.text:
Casting Call: The Chaos

We are seeking talented and passionate actors (18+) to join our exciting new Indie project! This is a unique opportunity to be part of a creative and collaborative production, utilizing **virtual production techniques** and **green screen technology**.

Requirements:

- Must be 18 years or older

- Comfortable performing in front of a green screen

- Enthusiastic about participating in an indie, creative-driven environment

Details:

- This is an unpaid project, but it offers a great chance to build your portfolio and gain experience in virtual production.

- Flexible scheduling for green screen scenes.

- A fantastic opportunity to work with a dedicated team on a passion project.

-IMDb Credit

If you're excited to bring unique characters to life in an innovative way, we'd love to hear from you!

To Apply:

Please submit a headshot, resume, and a brief video introduction.

They do not have to be professional!

We are looking for someone to portray these characters!

More information will be given after submission:

Chris presents himself as calm, confident, and even comforting. His tone is measured — he doesn’t command; he invites. He speaks like a leader or preacher, someone used to controlling a room through subtle persuasion rather than force. The steady eyes, careful pouring, and soft assurances suggest someone who knows how to perform sincerity.

Underneath the calm surface, there’s a manipulative intent.

Chris Myers (African American ages 20-30)

https://form.jotform.com/250471188877166

items.text:
Rola główna — wymagająca

Do krótkometrażowego filmu fabularnego poszukujemy aktorki do roli siedemnastoletniej dziewczyny. Rola płatna.
 
Bohaterka impulsywna i wrażliwa, ma w sobie jasność, ciepło i energię, które przyciągają ludzi. Reaguje szybko, mocno, czasem za bardzo. W jej ruchach i spojrzeniach jest napięcie, ale też delikatność, która łatwo się kruszy. Rola pełna emocjonalnych przemian, wymagająca naturalności i odwagi w odsłonięciu siebie.
 
Fizyczność:
• 17–20 lat (mniej więcej)
• drobna sylwetka, delikatne rysy
• czarne włosy, jasne oczy
• w przypadku innego koloru włosów – za zgodą aktorki, możliwość farbowania na czarno
• twarz o wyrazistej mimice
• ekspresja ciała: żywa, spontaniczna, z potencjałem do zatrzymania i ciszy
 
Zgłoszenia tylko na e-mail: (CV, zdjęcia – portret i sylwetka – oraz ewentualny link do demo reel lub krótkiego self-tape’a) prosimy przesyłać na adres:
nppcasting@gmail.com
 
 
Zdjęcia referencyjne poniżej

Want to learn how to transition from doing music into Acting?
Or how to get your music in TV and Film? 

BBR Indie Films is thrilled to announce our Celebrity Guest  Panelist- Gary "LIL G" Jenkins! 

​Gary "LIL G" is a National Platinum Recording Artist (lead singer of the R&B super-group SILK), Producer, Songwriter, and Actor.

​His impressive acting credits include:
🎬 Madea's Family Reunion (Stage Play)
🎬 Sleepy Hollow
🎬 Christmas Bae (coming soon)

​Don't miss the chance to hear from a true industry veteran at our next event, we are giving all the tea. Come ready to network, we ALWAYS have several Music Supervisors in the house.

​📅 Wed, October 29th, 2025
📍 Studio Movie Grill - Marietta, GA
⏱️ 6:00 PM - 10:00 PM
👻 In the theme of Halloween. Costumes are welcomed but not required. Best Costume wins a prize. 

​Secure your tickets and learn more about BBR Indie Films at bbrindiefilms.com and on Eventbrite!

Want to learn how to transition from doing music into Acting?
Or how to get your music in TV and Film? 

BBR Indie Films is thrilled to announce our Celebrity Guest  Panelist- Gary "LIL G" Jenkins! 

​Gary "LIL G" is a National Platinum Recording Artist (lead singer of the R&B super-group SILK), Producer, Songwriter, and Actor.

​His impressive acting credits include:
🎬 Madea's Family Reunion (Stage Play)
🎬 Sleepy Hollow
🎬 Christmas Bae (coming soon)

​Don't miss the chance to hear from a true industry veteran at our next event, we are giving all the tea. Come ready to network, we ALWAYS have several Music Supervisors in the house.

​📅 Wed, October 29th, 2025
📍 Studio Movie Grill - Marietta, GA
⏱️ 6:00 PM - 10:00 PM
👻 In the theme of Halloween. Costumes are welcomed but not required. Best Costume wins a prize. 

​Secure your tickets and learn more about BBR Indie Films at bbrindiefilms.com and on Eventbrite!

items.text:
📸 2 STATISTER SØGES TIL FOTOOPTAGELSER I KOLDING

Pga sygdom mangler jeg 2 statister til en fotooptagelse på Comwell Kolding i morgen mandag den 20. oktober. Billederne skal bruges i markedsføringsøjemed for Comwell Hotels – primært til promovering af møder og konferencer.

Køn: Mænd og kvinder

Alder: 35 år og opefter

Hvornår: Mandag den 20. oktober 2025

Tid: Kl. 8.30–16.00

Sted: Comwell Kolding, Skovbrynet 1, 6000 Kolding

Din rolle: Mødedeltager og/eller forretningsrejsende

Dresscode: Casual business 

Forplejning: Morgenmad, frokost og eftermiddagsforplejning er inkluderet

Der vil være stylist og makeupartist til stede, som hjælper med et naturligt og professionelt look på dagen. Dog skal alle statister selv medbringe 2-3 sæt tøj jfr dresscode: Casual business.

Det er vigtigt, at du selv kan komme til og fra location, og at du selv står for transportomkostninger.

Honorar

Som tak for din medvirken modtager du et gavekort til Comwell Hotels på 1.500 kr. Bemærk, at værdien indberettes som B-indkomst til SKAT i henhold til gældende lovgivning.

Er du frisk?

så send hurtigst muligt en mail til LN@comwell.com med følgende:

• Fulde navn og kontaktoplysninger

• Alder

• Et eller flere nyere billeder i fuld profil (uden filter)

Billederne viser stemninger fra tidligere shoots og bruges kun som eksempel.

items.text:
OPEN CASTING CALL

Rose Waite Studio are looking for inter-generational pairs who share a genuine love of theatre to feature in a filmed story for The Guardian and a paid partner. You will get the chance to watch a live theatre show from the opera box at one of Lloyd Webber’s theatres.

You could be a grandparent and grandchild, friends or colleagues etc. who share a genuine love of theatre to feature in a filmed story for The Guardian and a paid partner. 

You’ll need to be based in or near London. 

This is a paid opportunity. 

If you’d like to be filmed sharing your story, email stories@rosewaite.com with details of your story together and why theatre matters to you both.

Shoot dates: 24 & 25 November

Thank you!

🎬 CASTING CALL – MUSIC VIDEO 

From IES, a small independent LA-based team, comes a cinematic, collaborative project featuring the music of Emmarose Driver and directed by the talented Isabelle Paquett.

📅 Production Date: November 15–16 (Rehearsals), November 21–23 (Filming)�⏳ Casting Closes: November 23, 2025
📍 Location: Pacific Palisades, Los Angeles, CA, USA
💰 Pay: Unpaid 
🏷 Union Status: Not Applicable
🎥 Production Company: IES – Small Independent Team
🔗 IES on Vimeo

ABOUT THE PROJECT
This music video draws inspiration from 80’s summer camp murder mysteries – equal parts sexy, eerie, and nostalgic – with a simmering coming-of-age tension. The story will unfold across striking visuals designed for festival submissions and professional reels.

SEEKING TALENT 
🎭 Playing Age: 21–27 (must look college-age)
Roles Available:

👱‍♂️ 3 Male Actors
 • One tall with dark features
 • Two with open look/ethnicity

👩 2 Female Actors
 • Must have expressive, grounded, natural presence
🎓 Ideal for emerging talent eager to build their reel and gain festival exposure.

WHAT’S INCLUDED
🎞 Credit
📸 Footage for Reel

📩 HOW TO APPLY:

🎭 Apply for this casting as a Talent PRO member at Actors and Extras with a 1-month FREE trial period.

👉 Visit [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)
Create your own FREE profile and GET NOTIFIED of castings in your area.

Join [www.actorsandextras.com](https://www.actorsandextras.com) today!

🔍 This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.

🎶Offering Free VIRTUAL Voice & Acting Lessons!🎶

Hi! I'm Colleen and I'm a music theatre voice teacher, and the owner of Virtuoso Studios. We are proud to have a team of dedicated and experienced teachers who are passionate about helping students discover the joy of music. 

We currently offer lessons in voice, piano, acting, violin, viola, cello, and guitar, along with 2 in person recitals each year in MI, WI, IL, and MO. Each of our teachers is committed to providing personalized instruction to help every student reach their goals. Whether you’re preparing for auditions, looking to grow as a performer, or simply want to enjoy making music, our teachers are here to support and encourage you every step of the way!

Try a free lesson today! This is a great way to meet one of our teachers, experience a lesson, and see how music can be a fun and meaningful part of your life.

If you’d like to get started, fill out this form, and we’ll match you with the teacher who’s the best fit for your goals and interests. [www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons](https://www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons)

items.text:
## **Nørrebro Teater søger børn i alderen 8-12 år til kommende forestilling **

På vegne af Nørrebro Teater leder jeg efter børn, der har lyst til at medvirke i en forestilling med prøvestart i uge 45. Forestillingen har premiere d. 22. november, og spilleperioden er frem til d. 17. januar. 

Medvirken indebærer: 
* Medvirken i 1-2 scener i hver anden forestilling, så man ikke er på hver aften
* Det vil være med replikker
* Det vil være med sang. Man skal føle sig komfortabel med at synge, men behøver ikke at synge rent.

Hvis det har interesse, vil jeg se frem til at høre fra dig. Send mig en video med en kort præsentation samt uddrag af sang efter eget valg til [Amalieloof@gmail.com](mailto:Amalieloof@gmail.com)

Deadline er fredag d. 24. oktober kl. 12 og går man videre til fysisk audition, afholdes denne onsdag d. 29. oktober kl. 15 på Nørrebro Teater.

items.text:
**MSP SØGER 2 SKUESPILLERE (ULØNNET)**

Kære alle! Vi er et hold fra Multiplatform Storytelling and Production (MSP) i Aarhus, og skal i gang med en kort 1 dags produktion, stilet efter HBO’s “The Outsider”.

📌 **Logline**

*En lille dreng er blevet brutalt myrdet, og en efterforskningsleder forsøger at presse svar ud af det eneste vidne. *

Produktionen indebærer to korte scener; en forhørsscene, og en scene i skoven, dagen hvor liget blev fundet. 

Til dette projekt leder vi efter følgende. Køn og alder er underordnet, om du er 20 eller 60, så send en mail:
* **Detektiven** - mørk sindet noir-type, og lederen af efterforskningen. 
* **Vidnet** - forskræmt hunde gænger og personen der fandt liget. 

**Optagelser foregår Mandag d. 27. oktober.**

📅Tidspunktet vil være mellem 9 til 17.

📍 Alle optagelser vil foregå i Aarhus. 

Der vil være forsyninger og forplejning på set, naturligvis. 

Hvis det vækker interesse for jer, så kontakt mig, Harald Ruby (producer) på:
* [MkuuAngel@gmail.com](mailto:MkuuAngel@gmail.com)
* +45 42491424

Send jeres navn, alder, vellignende billeder, samt evt. erfaring (erfaring ikke påkrævet). 

Vi håber meget I vil være med!

Harald Ruby, Anna Brahe, Anja Skov, Laurits Klinke, Valdemar Hauritz, og Victor Panduro.

# **⚔️ Soldiers – Altamont, NY (Oct 20–25)**

Hi everyone! My name is **Sarah Morgan**, and I’m a producer on the indie medieval fantasy comedy feature film ***The Kingdom of Rexmonte***. We’ll be filming in **Altamont, NY** from **October 20–25**, and we’re looking for enthusiastic volunteers to play **soldiers** in battle scenes!

 🍴 Full lunch & snacks provided
 🎭 Ren faire/medieval attire welcome
 🙌 Unpaid, but an epic film set experience!

👉 Sign up here: [[https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9](https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9)](https://forms.gle/zqWmXjAw7sDqFRGv9) 

Also, please feel free to send the flyer and Google Form around to any groups or anyone you know who may be interested. We hope to see you on set!

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR A STUDENT SHORT-FILM!

Hi hi! My name is Megan Veto and I am a student at the Aurora Community College and will serve as the Writer/Director of this project. I am in need of actors/actresses for my Production 1 project! This will be unpaid, though I will provide anyone interested with a final version of the film. You will also be fed, so please let me know of any allergies or specific diets you may have!

Title: On the Rocks
Genre: Romantic Comedy
Logline: An angry bride walks into a bar and shakes up Ramos’s day.

SHOOTING DAYS: November 8th (10a - 6p) - 9th (1p - 7p)

LOCATION: 9075 E Lowry Blvd Denver, CO 80230

CHARACTERS:

-Ramos: The bartender. Late 20’s - early 30’s. Calm, cool, and collected. Takes care of his patrons. Wardrobe will be all black and a black button-up shirt.

-Sarah: The angry bride. Mid - late 20’s. Feisty, knows what she wants, but eventually softens under Ramos’s care. Please let me know what your dress size is so I can find a bride’s dress that fits! 😁

-Mike: The ex. Mid - 20’s. Flustered, desperately looking for Sarah. Cheated. Wardrobe will be black slacks and a nice white button-down shirt.

-Ruth: Sarah’s mom. 50’s. Helps Mike look for Sarah. Wardrobe will be a nice dress.

Please email me at megveto96@gmail.com with your headshot and demo reel, I will send you the script to read over.

Thank you so muc

**CASTING CALL (No-Budget Production)**
�- studentische Produktion� 

ACHTUNG ACHTUNG! 🐟 🌊 

Für das Projekt "FISHING FLIES" der Masterklasse Film & TV der FH St. Pölten suchen wir ab sofort nach drei Schauspieler*innen, die dem Film mit ihrer Präsenz ein wenig Leben einhauchen wollen😊 

**HARD FACTS:**
* Absurder Kurzfilm
* 6 Drehtage Anfang Jänner 2026
## **3 Schauspieler:innnen gesucht**
* Für ILSEBILL: Frau, 40 - 60 J. (ab 1,70m)
* Für MENNO: Mann, 20 - 30 J. (bis 1,70m)
* Für WILMUR BUTT: Mann, 40 - 60 J.

**DIE ROLLEN:**
* **Unsere erste Rolle ist "ILSEBILL".** 
Für unsere kampflustige Wissenschaftlerin suchen wir eine Frau im Alter von 40-60 Jahren und einer Größe ab 1,70m. 🧳🕹 

* **"MENNO" ist unsere nächste Rolle, die es zu **besetzen gilt! 
Für unseren impulsiven Agenten suchen wir nach einem Schauspieler im Alter von 20-30 Jahren und mit einer Größe bis 1,70m! 🕴🔎 

* **Und zu guter Letzt: "WILMUR BUTT"! **
Für unseren skurrilen "Fischbringer" suchen wir nach einem Schauspieler im Alter von 40-60 Jahren. 🐟💎 

Schreibt uns gerne direkt hier auf Facebook, an fishingflies.production@gmail.com oder meldet euch direkt bei unserem Casting-Team unter der Nummer +43 680 311 0685!  

Fish Out!🐟

Casting Call 📣 

Wir suchen die Gesichter für unsere Haupt- und Nebenrollen! Du findest, du passt perfekt zu einer dieser Figuren? Dann melde dich bei uns! Ganz einfach via Mail deine Bewerbung an casting@datingoffline.de senden 📨 

Drehzeitraum wird zwischen dem 24.11 und 05.12 sein (genauere Infos folgen), gedreht wird in Wiesbaden/Frankfurt und Umgebung 🎥

Wir sind ein junges und motiviertes Team, das Lust auf eine erfolgreiche und unvergessliche Zeit am Set haben - wir freuen uns, dich dabei zu haben! 

Findet mehr auf Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/datingoffline.shortfilm?igsh=MWE2ZHE5aGdhNThsaQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr

items.text:
**CASTING CALL** 

Til en musikvideo søger vi:
**1 mand mellem 50–70 år**
**1 kvinde mellem 50–70 år**

Jobbet er ulønnet

📍 **Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus d. 06/11**

Erfaring med skuespil er ikke et krav – der er tale om en mindre rolle.

📩 Ved interesse, send en mail med et billede til:
**nicotp@live.dk**

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig! 🙌
